{"tid":1416833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 你知唔知，場運動就快輸？ （8月5version）","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:54:47.000Z","uid":203845,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a62552c89e0efb6393192b24023db2c9d78633","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:37:27.000Z","msg":"8月5日全民大罷工，罷工係成功嘅，<br />\n但係林鄭依然用強硬姿態回應，<br />\n代表林鄭無視民意最後通牒，<br />\n直接同市民宣戰。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂<br />\n我方手足經過兩個月<br />\n無間斷抗爭同被官警打壓，<br />\n都開始出現新嘅問題。<br />\n唔解決，可能會導致運動直接死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問題包括以下</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n1.狗狗每日都開記者會<br />\n試圖挽回中間派支持同抹黑抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.對家想抹黑我地場運動由五大訴求<br />\n變成港獨，從而失去中間派支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 前線手足用火，被自己友(鬼？)批評，損失淺黃支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 警犬用盡方法激嬲我地<br />\n e. g. 天水圍女義士事件，公務員宿舍事件<br />\n希望令我地犯錯，然後一次過大逆轉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然以上問題唔係冇得救<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 文宣要大台，成立民間記者會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣同遊行抗爭唔同，極度需要大台嘅名先可以真正入屋。<br />\n比起連儂牆，記者會直接入屋，滲透率高<br />\n一方面可以反駁狗狗嘅抹黑<br />\n另一方面仲可以攞出狗狗違法證據<br />\n e.g. 展示過期催淚彈殼，<br />\n無辜市民被扑爆頭嘅事件，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 甚至可以邀請無辜受傷市民上嚟分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n時間最好就789點嘅時候<br />\n大家都放工，一開電視就見到我地嘅記者會<br />\n夠晒入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 推五大訴求。做好文宣，何謂時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n的而且確，關於五大訴求嘅聲音喺不同嘅集會同遊行越嚟越少聽到。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我地依然係向住五大訴求進發，勿忘初衷。</span> <br />\n至於「光復香港，時代革命」就要拜託各位手足同民間記者會<br />\n說明同港獨一d關係都冇<br />\n時代革命本身來自世代革新，<span style=\"color: red;\"> 並唔係港獨口號。</span> <br />\n當然連登大部分手足都知，<br />\n但係唔熟梁天琦嘅，可能真係唔知咩嚟<br />\n為免誤會，麻煩大家解釋下<br />\n至於港獨，我相信會係最終最終嘅升級<br />\n現階段，亦唔需要咁快港獨住<br />\n一下子就用核彈，大家難接受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 目的導向，注意安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先唔係分化，但係真係有黃絲唔滿意放火<br />\n雖則連登仔個個都話放核彈都唔割蓆<br />\n又話真。香港人根本唔會割<br />\n但係事實上真係有一班終極和理非<br />\n唔支持放火(港媽，擔心仔女安危嗰堆) <br />\n<br />\n所以火一定唔可以燒到民居<br />\n如果唔係同警黑無差別攻擊市民一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔好成為自己最睇唔起嘅嗰種人</span> <br />\n<br />\n當然<span style=\"color: pink;\"> 有意義地放</span> ，咁就冇辦法啦<br />\nE. G. Roadblock,煙燻狗屋<br />\n利申：絕對唔支持大家玩火，大家千歧唔好以身試法<br />\n再帶頭盔，只係討論緊咩情況下失民意<br />\n純粹學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4.沉著應戰，切忌衝動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除咗我地升級咗，其實班狗都升級咗。<br />\n佢地識<span style=\"color: teal;\">誘敵反包圍</span> ，又或者用輿論拉民意<br />\n所以前線一定要冷靜be water <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔好做無意義破壞</span> ，<br />\n最重要都係要有強大嘅心境<br />\n只要我地唔犯錯，對家一尾做衰嘢<br />\n我地就唔會無啦啦輸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後：推民間自衞隊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨住民間記者會追擊黑警，市民會慢慢對黑警失去信心<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\"> 民間自衞隊就係站喺人民嗰邊嘅保護者</span> <br />\n可以用報料嘅形式，請求自衞隊幫手<br />\n當普通市民都受過自衞隊嘅幫忙<br />\n我地就真係可以聚集民意<br />\n同時令佢地唔再對抗爭者恐懼<br />\n亦都可以令黑警更難得民心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後最後<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b1a8f7687cdae2f0cc288af38688da2983e1c1","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"篇文少少長，希望各位睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e460bd4844ccdc7579d8073735ed73a4db5583a","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d174ae3954002e6604f30baff70fe1539e55412","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab0c52b85f81016f5e2914a974e306eb0f0108f","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cef2cba00ec83ddd5dab36652656d05606055e","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"話說，認同嘅幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca36ef6acc424ab40b0a1f54ad9bd5aaec2d7642","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0eace4c54fe377d355ceb05145d27a083047e0","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2315f4da5e2e2fa637774eeeb1573c36d59310","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:41:31.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbb514deb61e867b5284ff368dcb5d80269706a","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7817f90960c4ed85aa7f7020d8479fc8ca3b3a85","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8b49309f6da24304b76add1521f6fb679b79c5","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"大家如果認同，幫手推下呀，唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985edc740f08b2196593ca6751083006d1c42c84","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4343ac8e11d0950a25be1a606a623be1d90764a1","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1266b81131645432aa5c5548d5178d4ba61c59","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35afee427d1b52d1ca33fcc4e09cd2f1ef14ca66","tid":1416833,"uid":167290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"有point<br />\n一齊入黎plan點實踐！！！"},{"pid":"8b951ef17e325bfee9dcc58b2fd2814e44fbfa8b","tid":1416833,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35afee427d1b52d1ca33fcc4e09cd2f1ef14ca66","tid":1416833,"uid":167290,"like":1,"dislike":